      "content": "That's interesting. You mentioned that Profile B might be seen as a \"higher risk\" because of his employment and education history. Do you think those specific factors (job history and education) are actually more predictive of future criminal behavior than the stable background of Profile A, or is there some other underlying reason a judge would see them differently?",
